
         BeV Memcache FS - Memcache FileSystem
_______________________________________________________________________________



BeV Memcache FS is a file system for memcached based on FUSE. 

This project is a fork of Tsukasa Hamano <code@cupsy.org>'s memcachefs project.


/!\ Warning!
------------
    
BeV Memcache FS is meant to be used as a single point of entry for your
memcached data.

Bev Memcache FS will store the file metadata in the keys of memcached.
You won't be able to access Memcache's data from another client than your
mounted file system easilly.
        




